Interface BusinessModel

All Superinterfaces:
ModelObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
BusinessModelImpl
public interface BusinessModel
extends ModelObject

A representation of the model object 'Business Model'.

The following features are supported:

  • Parent Model
  • Physical Model
  • Tables
  • Relationships
